<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 50 actions you can do.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Smooth animation]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animated with Spine2D technology (<strong>1280p 60fps</strong>).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Camera Effect]</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >POV Camera Effects </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camera shake Night-to-morning transition/vice-versa. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>[Appearance change]</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hairstyle Hair Color Eye color Panties Socks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194110/extras/c8d607be05651a277c8132829ed513a6.avif?t=1744469849\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194110/extras_big/c8d607be05651a277c8132829ed513a6.avif?t=1744469849 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>X-ray/Cross-Section view in different spots!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194110/extras/5782ed1f5d828252117ef718a665e50a.avif?t=1744469849\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194110/extras_big/5782ed1f5d828252117ef718a665e50a.avif?t=1744469849 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reveal her naughty side!</strong>  <br>Restraints!  <br>Assault her mouth!  <br>Make her messy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194110/extras/294424812764dea20a22fbe8d9ef89c5.avif?t=1744469849\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st